snippet.title: Longplay of SpongeBob SquarePants: Battle for Bikini Bottom
snippet.description:
Longplay of SpongeBob SquarePants: Battle for Bikini Bottom, played as the NTSC version on the GameCube. This game's version was released on Oct. 31st, 2003. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

0:00:00 - Start
0:00:48 - Intro
0:04:26 - First Part of Bikini Bottom
0:15:15 - Jellyfish Fields
0:48:10 - Boss: Jellyfish King
0:49:45 - Jellyfish Fields continued
0:52:18 - Downtown Bikini Bottom
1:26:09 - Goo Lagoon
2:00:37 - Poseidome (Boss: Sandy)
2:07:04 - Second Part of Bikini Bottom
2:13:21 - Rock Bottom
2:47:33 - Sand Mountain
3:14:32 - Mermalair
3:37:21 - Boss: Prawn
3:42:41 - Industrial Park (Boss: Patrick)
3:50:54 - Jellyfish Fields (revisited)
3:55:16 - Downtown Bikini Bottom (revisited)
3:56:48 - Third Part of Bikini Bottom 
4:02:49 - Kelp Forest
4:34:41 - Flying Dutchman's Graveyard
4:53:14 - Boss: Flying Dutchman
4:58:11 - Spongebob's Dream
5:18:02 - Patrick & Mr. Krabs Spatula's
5:21:41 - Chum Bucket Lab (Final boss: Spongebob)
5:30:39 - Ending
5:33:08 - Special Ending (100 Golden Spatula's)
5:33:53 - Credits
